[32m│[0m 3. ✗ Raw path traversal `../../../../` - Returns 404 (blocked)               [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m 4. ✗ Mixed patterns with `/./` - Returns 404 (blocked)                       [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m **Key Findings:**                                                            [32m│[0m
